name: complex_if_branchwise_sub_same_condition
section: control-if-arithmetic
args: cond:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Subtracting two if expressions with the same condition must choose the branchwise difference.
law: (= (fuzz-sub (if {cond} {a} {b}) (if {cond} {c} {d})) (if {cond} (fuzz-sub {a} {c}) (fuzz-sub {b} {d})))
